{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650780/extras/Key.png?t=1733527130\" /><strong>Cavern is an Action RPG with heavy Roguelike and Sandbox elements.</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650780/extras/Key.png?t=1733527130\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tackle procedurally generated levels and puzzles in a unique way by swapping out objects in real-time.</strong>\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Turn a rock into a bomb to clear terrain,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Turn a slime into a harmless pot,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Give an sword wielding skeleton a useless stick,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Turn cobwebs into a stalactite to fall on your enemy...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650780/extras/Pot.png?t=1733527130\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650780/extras/Rock.png?t=1733527130\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650780/extras/Bomb.png?t=1733527130\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Every situation presents a unique challenge and a unique solution whether you decide to fight or meddle. As you go deeper into the Cavern, the level generation becomes more chaotic, and the player gains more control...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650780/extras/Pot.png?t=1733527130\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650780/extras/Rock.png?t=1733527130\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650780/extras/Bomb.png?t=1733527130\" /><